	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I see that the cartridge has an entrance of sound, is possible to use it like entrance of DCPM or similar?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Cartridge_connector">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Cartridge_connector</a><!-- m -->

		

